    this.addProperty('firstName');
    this.addProperty('lastName');
    this.addProperty('email');
  }
}  In this example, the  UserModel  is configured with three properties that by default:   Can be watched for changes  Will be included when serializing / deserializing  Will be cloned if  clone()  is called

